Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到青焰魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚·布雷斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等贱民无有资格直呼其姓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 赛尔贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 加利亚士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有义务听从你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是加利亚之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走的是你们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安·盖伦斯本·雷金·莱布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子 正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此地非帝国地界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 亦不归属于加利亚所有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格说来 是赛尔贝莉亚所有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归属女武神族人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神族已经灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此言差矣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前的碑文便是明证
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭示了她们即将再次君临天下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要逮捕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛尔贝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 否则我就开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能砍断枪弹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:59.38,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(835,715)\fad(500,0)\4a&HFF\t(100,500,\4a&H80)\t(4090,4490,\4a&HFF)}被揭开的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有类似地鸣的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鸣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨 必要之物已为我所有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝国军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遗迹倒塌前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 马克西米利安的话让人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去确认后马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 他们真打算毁了巴里亚斯遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 头顶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何这么问 殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾又从这世上消灭一座与你有缘之物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下是我唯一寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范乌哲可有消息？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请换上脚下的便装 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军装会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 死在这里的话有负达蒙将军之托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 怎么会找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工业区完好无损吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 有消息称司令官已经落网
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无任何策略思想可言 对待战斗漫不经心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个披着军装的酒囊饭袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留他何用 杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想干什么 我是奉达蒙将军之命！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被岩石的棱角砸破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 骨头没有断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只能临时包扎下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽早离开这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿有通往外界的洞口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能推动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎全凭上天赐予的奇迹般的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望维尔金也平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会没事的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我 连累你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副世界末日般的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 肯定会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是维尔金啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 法尔迪奥应该最清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金有多么不同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是做些不循常理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次遇见他时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在逃难 他却在不慌不忙的写生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 刚进大学时有一件关于维尔金的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生中最漂亮的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生们都在打赌谁最先和她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 考古学是一种浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不妨也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又那么做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老师明明还在 那孩子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时出现了个超凡脱俗的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大跌眼镜 真真正正的一匹黑马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更让人大跌眼镜的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道维尔金对人家说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但肯定是很失礼的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你脸部的骨骼令人感兴趣”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“请务必让我写生”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 维尔金的厉害之处还在后面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终渐渐和她越走越近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为恋人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金完全没把人家当作异性看待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对方未必如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 即使这样 女孩也没有说过维尔金的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何能理解她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金人古怪 有时真让人为他着急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有某种奇妙的魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.26,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好牵强的理论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真理时常伴随着飞跃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再与现实抗争一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 队长 艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被埋在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我会救出他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么保证？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有也要救
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杳无回音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金 我们听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们那里情况怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 法尔迪奥受了点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是先塌陷还是先逃出生天 得和时间赛跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 沙漠中的夜晚很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 比他们外面三个好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜥…蜥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜥蜴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是去洞里躲避夜晚的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明附近有大小足够你们通过的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去问蜥蜴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会去找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护窝蜥蜴的触觉比人类灵敏几十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要护窝蜥蜴还和他们呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗迹就不会塌陷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来如果开始逃走的话就完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦尔特中士是悲观主义者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们第一小队的队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能理解我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥并非无视我作为达鲁库斯人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Ragnite 遗迹的石壁反射阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就告诉你们方位和角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个位置肯定有洞口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳快落山了 抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法保证
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢看我就踹你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股后面难道还长眼睛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 如果看了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管把我打进大牢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还算好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死胡同吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 艾丽西娅你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 法尔迪奥也没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还没挂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 一定救你们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在执行相同的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从挡道的岩石开始清理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也尽自己所能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害了对方？ 说我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘴里的“没事、不要紧”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有现实依据吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为未来是自己去创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有自己能保证它平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个过分的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对甩了的女人说“没事的”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她作出了最佳的选择 所以才没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她绝对能获得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:19:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 会亲口告诉她这些话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉新娘子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金 你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护窝蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是怎么给幼蜥喂食的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定想知道 这还用问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.43,0:20:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别卖关子 那是很珍贵的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长 你这伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段小小的冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么满身是泥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人担心死了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做好了蔬菜羹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合艾丽西娅的面包吃 香得没话说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.94,0:20:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃饭吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托疗伤 范乌哲情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如您想像的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奈没有太多值得向殿下报告的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中将对范乌哲方面的战果似乎颇为不满
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来未曾遇到那辆坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中将正为思恋它而心焦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不谈这些 中央有何指示？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼠辈们在吵吵嚷嚷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 短时间内我们也不会无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想见你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.84,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飞奔出门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:56.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}思い出は僕を　海辺に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:56.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}回忆将我 引向海边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:01.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:05.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:05.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘风飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心地良さばかりを　求めて生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一味追求安逸的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:20.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ぐるぐる同じ場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:20.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}原地踏步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}そんな僕の前に　現れた笑顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出现在我面前的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太陽のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像太阳般灿烂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想见你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飞奔出门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.61,0:22:48.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑い合えるように　唄い合えるように
